rows.label: bf09270100_0010
rows.name: Shin!

rows.label: bf09270100_0020
rows.name:
Are you alone?
Where's Metsu?

rows.label: bf09270100_0030
rows.name: He went ahead.

rows.label: bf09270100_0040
rows.name: Well then, what are you doing here?

rows.label: bf09270100_0050
rows.name: Waiting. For you.

rows.label: bf09270100_0060
rows.name:
For us?
Are you trying to stop us going after Metsu?

rows.label: bf09270100_0070
rows.name: Perhaps...

rows.label: bf09270100_0080
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf09270100_0090
rows.name: I want to see for myself.

rows.label: bf09270100_0100
rows.name: If this world has any will of its own...

rows.label: bf09270100_0110
rows.name: which one would it choose, you or Metsu...?

rows.label: bf09270100_0120
rows.name: Then...you should let us pass.

rows.label: bf09270100_0130
rows.name: That, I cannot do.

rows.label: bf09270100_0140
rows.name:
But why? In your state, you
should barely be able to stand!

rows.label: bf09270100_0150
rows.name: You know if we fight now, you'll...!

rows.label: bf09270100_0160
rows.name: You see right through me, Hikari.

rows.label: bf09270100_0170
rows.name:
...But I made a promise.
I'll do whatever it takes to fulfill his desire.

rows.label: bf09270100_0180
rows.name: Even if it means your death?

rows.label: bf09270100_0190
rows.name: Gladly.

rows.label: bf09270100_0200
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf09270100_0210
rows.name: It looks like we won't get past without a fight, chum.

rows.label: bf09270100_0220
rows.name:
Seems so.
We'll give it all we've got! C'mon!

rows.label: bf09270100_0230
rows.name:
As it should be.
Come at me, boy!
